        children: "Clarity Hub on Github"
      }), ". This included all of our original code pivots as well. While interviewing with a few startups, a couple asked me for details on Clarity Hub and how we approached the problem domain, architectural decisions, and software design. All these notes ended up as part of the README: ", _jsx(_components.a, {
